sical numerical\nsimulations. Our formalism may also be useful to study condensates of ultra\nlight bosonic dark matter, such as fuzzy dark matter, and axion stars, for\ninstance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Dec 2016 18:55:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 May 2017 23:54:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 20 Dec 2018 14:23:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-21"}
