al errors by 10%-20%,\ndepending on experimental specifications, and (4) other higher-order\ncontributions are negligible at least for near future experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Dec 2016 01:49:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2017 20:28:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 25 Nov 2019 19:00:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-27"}
